This file is the README for Pod::Html version 1.09_02

INSTALLATION

perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install

PREREQUISITES

(All of these are core)

  Carp
  Config
  Cwd
  File::Spec
  Getopt::Long
  locale

TESTING

This module requires the following modules for thorough testing:

  (These are core, you should be ok)
  File::Spec
  Test::More

  (These are optional, but very useful tools to have around)
  Test::Exception
  Test::Output

BUGS

Please report all bugs on the RT queue:

L<http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Pod-Html>

